t":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":337914,"user_name":"Geek_Linh","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2614358,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1B9BE2F4C5098A","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1647157704,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1647157704","product_id":100083301,"comment_content":"王老师好，我有一个疑问是个人的稳定理财利率怎么理解？这个是否也会随着经验、见识的增长而变化？现在房贷的利率是比较稳定好预估的，但是个人的理财能力是会有变化的。“稳定”的理财利率如何去量化？希望能够得到您的解答，谢谢。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":329269,"user_name":"Allanxl","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1208573,"ip_address":"","ucode":"8C1146D2C30C5B","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/70/fd/0e1655d1.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1641263368,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1641263368","product_id":100083301,"comment_content":"“如果你的稳定理财利率能够高于房贷贷款利率，那么首付少付、还款年限长合适”<br><br>这句话有点问题。因为房贷是单利（不会利滚利），投资是复利（收益继续产生收益），所以理财利率略低于房贷贷款利率时，仍然最终收益更大；并且还款年限越长，复利和单利差越大。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":326179,"user_name":"充电中","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1246337,"ip_address":"","ucode":"EAB79647E8A159","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/04/81/622a1a4e.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1639406581,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1639406581","product_id":100083301,"comment_content":"老师，房价程序里面求每月还款金额数的代码没理解，可以解释下吗？<br>源代码里是<br>monthly_repayment = float(mortgage) * mortgage_monthly_rate * ((1 + mortgage_monthly_rate) ** (12 * mortgage_years)) &#47; ((1 + mortgage_monthly_rate) ** (12 * mortgage_years) - 1)<br>我理解是用最终需还款金额&#47;月份得到每月需还款金额数，也就是<br>monthly_repayment = float(mortgage) *  ((1 + mortgage_monthly_rate) ** (12 * mortgage_years)) &#47; (12 * mortgage_years)，<br>求老师解释下，或者指点下我哪里思考错了，感谢","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":318296,"user_name":"loading ...","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2303336,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D1E3A2D6235E69","user_header":